# Tool Bar
-> Move tool -> V  -> We can move and select the objects in canvas
   -> Hand tool -> H  -> We can move the objects in canvas without clicking
   -> Scale tool -> K  -> We can scale the object bigger or smaller [As equal]

-> Frame tool -> F -> First we should select the frames to develop for moblie app and websites
   -> Section tool  Shift+S  -> It would use to organize the frames. IF you want make it all the frames as a group, click on section and select [Change the background colour if frames not appear]
   -> Slice tool  -> S -> It would to export the specific object -> you will look at 55.00 min in part 1 video

-> Rectangle tool -> R -> We can create Rectangle   [we can watch video at 1.16]
    -> line tool -> L  -> We can draw the line
    -> Arrow  -> Shift+L  -> We can draw the Arrow
    -> Elipse -> o  -> We can draw Elipse
    -> Star  -> We can add the star
    -> Image -> We can upload the image from local

-> Pen Tool -> We can draw manually
    -> Pencil tool -> We can draw manually 

-> Text tool -> We can write the text

-> comment tool -> We can write the comment

-> Plugins  tool



